\c 15
\s UAbisalomu uvukela uDavida
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokhu uAbisalomu wazilungisela izinqola lamabhiza, labantu abangamatshumi amahlanu begijima phambi kwakhe\x + 1 Kho. 1.5.\x*.
\v 2 UAbisalomu wayesevuka ekuseni kakhulu eme eceleni kwendlela yesango; kwakusithi wonke umuntu olecala lomthetho eliya enkosini ukwahlulelwa, uAbisalomu ambize athi: Ungowawuphi umuzi? Lapho esithi: Inceku yakho ingowesinye sezizwe zakoIsrayeli;
\v 3 uAbisalomu abesesithi kuye: Bona, indaba zakho zinhle zilungile, kodwa kakho owenkosi ukuthi akuzwe.
\v 4 UAbisalomu abesesithi: Kungathi ngabe ngibekwe umahluleli elizweni, ukuthi wonke umuntu olecala lomthetho lodaba angeza kimi, njalo bengizamlungisela\x + Hlu. 9.29.\x*.
\v 5 Kwakusithi lapho kusondela umuntu ukumkhothamela, elule isandla sakhe, ambambe, amange.
\v 6 UAbisalomu wasesenza ngalindlela kuIsrayeli wonke, bona abeza enkosini ukwahlulelwa; ngalokho uAbisalomu wathumba\f + \fk wathumba: \fl Heb. \fqa weba\f* inhliziyo yamadoda akoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 7 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kweminyaka engamatshumi amane uAbisalomu wathi enkosini: Ake ngiyekhokha isithembiso sami engasithembisa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni eHebroni\x + 1 Sam. 16.1.\x*.
\v 8 Ngoba inceku yakho yathembisa isithembiso\x + Gen. 28.20,21.\x* ngisahlala eGeshuri eSiriya ngisithi: Uba iN\nd kosi\nd* ingibuyisela lokungibuyisela eJerusalema, ngizayikhonza iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 13.38.\x*.
\v 9 Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Hamba ngokuthula. Wasesukuma waya eHebroni\x + 1 Sam. 1.17.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Kodwa uAbisalomu wathuma izinhloli ezizweni zonke zakoIsrayeli esithi: Lapho lisizwa ukukhala kophondo, lizakuthi: UAbisalomu uyinkosi eHebroni!
\v 11 Kwasekuhamba loAbisalomu amadoda angamakhulu amabili esuka eJerusalema, anxusiweyo\x + 1 Sam. 9.13. 1 Sam. 16.3,5.\x*, ahamba ebuqothweni bawo, njalo engazi lutho\x + Gen. 20.5. 1 Kho. 22.34.\x*.
\v 12 UAbisalomu wasethumela \add wabiza\add* uAhithofeli weGilo\x + 15.31. 16.20. 17.1,14,23. 11.3. 23.34.\x*, umeluleki kaDavida\x + 1 Lan. 27.33. Hlab. 41.9. 55.12,13,14.\x*, esuka emzini wakhe, eGilo\x + Josh. 15.51.\x*, esahlaba imihlatshelo. Njalo ugobe lwaqina, labantu bahamba banda\x + Hlab. 3.1.\x* kuAbisalomu\x + 3.1. Eks. 19.19.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kwasekufika isithunywa kuDavida, sisithi: Inhliziyo yabantu bakoIsrayeli ilandela uAbisalomu\x + 15.6. Hlu. 9.3.\x*.
\v 14 Wasesithi uDavida ezincekwini zakhe zonke ezazilaye eJerusalema: Sukumani, sibaleke, ngoba kasilakuphepha ebusweni bukaAbisalomu\x + 19.9. Hlab. 3.\x*. Phangisani ukuhamba, hlezi aphangise asifice, asehlisele\f + \fk sehlisele: \fl Heb. \fqa awisele phezu kwethu\f* okubi, atshaye umuzi ngobukhali benkemba.
\v 15 Izinceku zenkosi zasezisithi enkosini: Njengakho konke inkosi, inkosi yami, ekukhethayo, khangela, \add nanzi\add* inceku zakho.
\v 16 Yasiphuma inkosi, layo yonke indlu yayo iyilandela. Inkosi yasitshiya abafazi abalitshumi, abafazi abancane, ukuze balinde indlu\x + 16.21,22.\x*.
\v 17 Yasiphuma inkosi, labo bonke abantu beyilandela; bema endlini ekhatshana.
\v 18 Lazo zonke inceku zayo zedlula eceleni kwayo, njalo wonke amaKerethi\x + 1 Sam. 30.14.\x* lawo wonke amaPelethi\x + 8.18.\x* lawo wonke amaGiti, amadoda angamakhulu ayisithupha, eza amlandela evela eGati\x + 1 Sam. 27.2. 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*, edlula phambi kwenkosi.
\p
\v 19 Inkosi yasisithi kuIthayi umGiti\x + 18.2.\x*: Lawe uhambelani lathi? Buyela uhlale lenkosi, ngoba ungowezizweni njalo ungumxotshwa endaweni yakho\x + 2 Kho. 17.23. 24.14. 25.21. Amos 1.5. 6.7.\x*.
\v 20 Ufike izolo; pho, lamuhla ngikuzulazulise ngokuhamba lathi, njengoba ngiya lapho engiya khona? Buyela ubuyisele abafowenu. Umusa leqiniso kakube lawe\x + 1 Sam. 23.13.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa uIthayi wayiphendula inkosi wathi: Kuphila kukaJehova, njalo kuphila kwenkosi yami\x + Ruthe 3.13. Ruthe 1.16,17.\x*, inkosi, isibili kuleyondawo lapho inkosi yami, inkosi, ezakuba kiyo, loba kusekufeni loba kusekuphileni, lalapho izakuba khona inceku yakho.
\v 22 UDavida wasesithi kuIthayi: Hamba, uchaphe\x + 15.23.\x*. UIthayi umGiti wasechapha kanye labantu bakhe bonke labantwanyana ababelaye.
\v 23 Ilizwe lonke lakhala inyembezi ngelizwi elikhulu, njalo abantu bonke bachapha. Inkosi yasichapha isifula iKidroni\x + 1 Kho. 2.37. 15.13. 2 Kho. 23,4,6,12. 2 Lan. 15.16. 29.16. 30.14. Jer. 31.40.\x*, labantu bonke bachapha, ngasendleleni yenkangala\x + 15.28. 16.2. 17.16,29.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Njalo khangela, uZadoki laye lawo wonke amaLevi elaye\x + 8.17. 20.25. 1 Kho. 4.4.\x*, bethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu\x + Nani 4.15.\x*, bawubeka phansi umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu\x + Josh. 7.23.\x*; uAbhiyatha wasesenyuka\x + 20.25. 1 Sam. 22.20. 23.6,9. 1 Kho. 4.4.\x*, abantu bonke baze baphela ukudlula bephuma emzini.
\v 25 Inkosi yasisithi kuZadoki: Buyisela umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu emzini. Uba ngizathola umusa emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, izangibuyisa\x + Hlab. 43.3.\x* ingitshengise wona kanye lendawo yayo yokuhlala\x + Eks. 15.13. Jer. 25.30.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa uba isitsho njalo, \add ithi\add*: Kangithokozi ngawe\x + 22.20. Nani 14.8. 1 Kho. 10.9. 2 Lan. 9.8. Hlab. 18.19. 22.8. Isa. 62.4.\x*; khangela ngi\add lapha\add*, kayenze kimi njengokuhle emehlweni ayo\x + Hlu. 10.15.\x*.
\v 27 Inkosi yasisithi kuZadoki umpristi: Ungumboni yini\x + 1 Sam. 9.9.\x*? Buyela emzini ngokuthula, loAhimahazi indodana yakho loJonathani indodana kaAbhiyatha, amadodana enu womabili elani\x + 15.36. 17.17. 18.19,27. 1 Kho. 1.42. 4.15. 1 Lan. 6.8,53.\x*.
\v 28 Bona, ngizalinda emazibukweni enkangala, kuze kufike ilizwi elivela kini lokungibikela\x + 2.29. 4.7. 17.16. Josh. 5.10. 18.18. 2 Kho. 25.4,5. Jer. 39.4,5. 52.7,8.\x*.
\v 29 Ngakho uZadoki loAbhiyatha bawubuyisela umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu eJerusalema, bahlala khona.
\p
\v 30 UDavida wasesenyuka ngomqanso wemihlwathi, esenyuka ekhala inyembezi, embomboze ikhanda lakhe\x + 19.4. Esta 6.12. Jer. 14.3,4.\x*, wahamba engelamanyathela\x + Isa. 20.2,4.\x*; labo bonke abantu ababelaye bambomboza, ngulowo lalowo ikhanda lakhe, benyuka, besenyuka bekhala inyembezi\x + 5.10. Hlab. 126.6.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Kwasekubikwa kuDavida kwathiwa: UAhithofeli uphakathi kwabakugobe loAbisalomu. UDavida wasesithi: N\nd kosi\nd*, ake enze icebo likaAhithofeli\x + 16.23. 17.14,23.\x* libe yibuthutha.
\p
\v 32 Kwasekusithi uDavida esefike engqongeni lapho ayekhonza khona uNkulunkulu, khangela, uHushayi umArki wamhlangabeza\x + Josh. 16.2.\x*, isembatho sakhe sidatshuliwe\x + 1.2.\x*, lenhlabathi isekhanda lakhe\x + Josh. 7.6.\x*.
\v 33 UDavida wasesithi kuye: Uba usedlula lami, uzakuba ngumthwalo kimi\x + 19.35.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa uba ubuyela emzini uthi kuAbisalomu: Ngizakuba yinceku yakho, nkosi\x + 16.19.\x*; kade ngiyinceku kayihlo, kodwa khathesi sengizakuba yinceku yakho; khona uzangichithela icebo likaAhithofeli\x + Hlab. 33.10.\x*.
\v 35 Njalo kabakho yini kanye lawe lapho oZadoki loAbhiyatha abapristi? Ngakho kuzakuthi yonke indaba oyizwayo endlini yenkosi, uyitshele oZadoki loAbhiyatha abapristi\x + 17.15,16.\x*.
\v 36 Khangela, kukhona lapho kanye labo amadodana abo amabili, uAhimahazi okaZadoki, loJonathani okaAbhiyatha; njalo uzathumela ngesandla sabo kimi yonke into ozayizwa\x + 15.27.\x*.
\v 37 UHushayi umngane kaDavida wasefika emzini\x + 16.16. 1 Lan. 27.33. 1 Kho. 4.5,16.\x*, loAbisalomu wafika eJerusalema\x + 16.15.\x*.